txt.en: 'I have kept my end of the agreement. The stores of Morgul blades will be made available to Lhaereth.'
'Soon, soon, oh Thargaun. Lhaereth's plague takes time.'
'Once the plague is unleashed, you shall command the greatest army of the dead!'
'We only hope that Gothmog has no sway over your decisions, as you have told our dear mistress this.'
'Gothmog is useless to me. I have only ever taken orders from the Witch-king and no other.'
'I make this pact as my dealings with Shalgoth have been barren.'
'Lhaereth is more cunning. We share the same goals, it would seem.'
'I can not wait for this plague. Bring the bodies of those you kill to my domain.'
'What was that?! Someone spies upon this meeting?! Kill them!'
'There, ahead. We must be careful and not alert them to our presence.'
